# Pull-Based Sync Protocol\n\nThis module provides a pull-based sync protocol for the hub federation.\n\n## Usage\n\n```python\nfrom hub.federation.sync_protocol import SyncProtocol\n\n# Create a new sync protocol instance\nprotocol = SyncProtocol()\n\n# Fetch manifests from peer repositories\nmanifests = protocol.fetch_manifests()\n\n# Sync lessons with peer repositories\nprotocol.sync_lessons(manifests)\n```
